Private RT
![image](https://github.com/JayPhantom/AWS-Cloud-Portfolio/assets/109772529/dc7cd9c4-ad22-42bb-b76f-b8147f6c7a95)

Associate the Public Route Table to the public subnet and the private route table to the private subnet. On the Public Route Table, attach the public route table to the InternetGateway.

![image](https://github.com/JayPhantom/AWS-Cloud-Portfolio/assets/109772529/81dc8b4f-51a4-42c0-9af7-09fc1d7a9a00)

